HEADWORD: Disproportionable
<hw>Dis`pro*por"tion*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Disproportional; unsuitable in form, size, quantity, or adaptation;
disproportionate; inadequate.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Dis`pro*por"tion*a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos>
<au>Hammond.</au> -- <wf>Dis`pro*por"tion*a*bly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

